{"type": "article", "id": 7187, "title": "Sushi Towels 寿司毛巾", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-09T07:35:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052341124n8oAXBKTj6ISsO2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是一条可爱的“寿司毛巾”，这款看起来普普通通的毛巾，经过巧妙的折叠，瞬间变成了一个寿司的模样，而且根据配色的不同，还分鲑鱼寿司，金枪鱼寿司，蟹肉寿司等等。对于寿司爱好者来说，买一打这样的毛巾放在厨房里面，恐怕会连食欲了增加不少吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052341110RQJmcYqbGAWZ9Hn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234112xKZIwt72OM9vepql.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}